<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:13:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日本放送协会称，一名男子袭击中国校车，造成日本妇女和儿童受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/man-attacks-school-bus-china-wounding-japanese-woman-child-nhk-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>据日本放送协会 (NHK) 报道，周一，一名疑似持刀男子袭击了中国苏州一所日本学校使用的一辆公交车，造成一名日本妇女和她的孩子受伤。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:45:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/man-attacks-school-bus-china-wounding-japanese-woman-child-nhk-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>波兰总统表示希望中国帮助乌克兰实现和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/polish-president-says-he-hopes-china-can-help-bring-peace-ukraine-2024-06-24/</link><description>波兰总统安杰伊·杜达周一在访问北京期间表示，他希望中国帮助找到尊重国际法的乌克兰和平解决方案。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/polish-president-says-he-hopes-china-can-help-bring-peace-ukraine-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国赣锋等矿业公司就墨西哥特许权提起仲裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/miners-including-chinas-ganfeng-launch-arbitration-case-against-mexico-over-2024-06-24/</link><description>根据世界银行争端解决中心的帖子，英国公司 Bacanora Lithium 和 Sonora Lithium 以及中国赣锋国际贸易公司就采矿特许权向墨西哥政府提起了仲裁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:27:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/miners-including-chinas-ganfeng-launch-arbitration-case-against-mexico-over-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国称俄罗斯可能正在讨论帮助朝鲜发展导弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-russia-could-be-discussing-help-north-korea-missile-development-2024-06-24/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周一表示，俄罗斯和朝鲜之间关于平壤向莫斯科提供武器的回报的讨论可能与朝鲜的核远程导弹开发有关。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-russia-could-be-discussing-help-north-korea-missile-development-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警称在争议岛屿附近“驱离”日本船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coastguard-says-it-drove-away-japanese-boats-near-disputed-islands-2024-06-24/</link><description>中国海警周一表示，已对6月20日至24日期间进入钓鱼岛“领海”的四艘日本渔船和几艘巡逻艇采取了“必要管控措施”并“驱离”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 12:44:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coastguard-says-it-drove-away-japanese-boats-near-disputed-islands-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>创纪录的降雨使中国南方城市长沙陷入瘫痪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/record-rains-paralyse-chinas-southern-city-changsha-2024-06-24/</link><description>周一，中国南方城市长沙遭遇大雨，道路变成河流，人行地下通道和地铁隧道被淹没。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 12:13:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/record-rains-paralyse-chinas-southern-city-changsha-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>快时尚零售商 Shein 于 6 月初申请伦敦上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fast-fashion-retailer-shein-filed-london-listing-early-june-sources-say-2024-06-24/</link><description>两位消息人士称，Shein 于 6 月初向英国市场监管机构秘密提交了文件，从而启动了这家在线快时尚零售商今年晚些时候可能在伦敦上市的进程。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 11:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fast-fashion-retailer-shein-filed-london-listing-early-june-sources-say-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>瑞银集团将向北京国资管理公司出售合资企业的部分股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ubs-sell-partial-stake-joint-venture-beijing-state-asset-manager-2024-06-24/</link><description>瑞银集团(UBS)正在将其一家证券合资企业的部分股权出售给北京国有资产管理公司(BSAM)，这是这家瑞士银行在与瑞信合并后巩固在华业务的关键一步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:58:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ubs-sell-partial-stake-joint-venture-beijing-state-asset-manager-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚葡萄酒行业是欧盟行业令人担忧的案例研究</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australian-wine-sector-worrying-case-study-eu-industries-china-trade-spat-2024-06-24/</link><description>行业高管表示，受到中国关税的打击，澳大利亚葡萄酒行业尽管忙于开拓新市场、从其他地方采购葡萄并寻求政府帮助，但仍难以抵消出口下降的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:22:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australian-wine-sector-worrying-case-study-eu-industries-china-trade-spat-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾指责中国使用“非法武力”故意扰乱补给任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-continue-south-china-sea-resupply-missions-defense-sec-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长表示，中国使用“侵略性和非法武力”扰乱了在南海的补给任务，并表示上周造成一名水手受伤的海上事件既不是误会，也不是意外。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 06:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-continue-south-china-sea-resupply-missions-defense-sec-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>英国高级法官在外国法官争吵中审理香港抗议案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/top-british-judge-hears-hong-kong-protest-case-amid-foreign-judges-row-2024-06-24/</link><description>周一，一名英国高级法官在香港审理了一起涉及七名知名民主党人的抗议相关案件，加剧了关于外国法官是否应该在国家安全镇压期间继续担任香港最高法院法官的争论。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 05:44:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/top-british-judge-hears-hong-kong-protest-case-amid-foreign-judges-row-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国字节跳动与博通合作开发先进人工智能芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-bytedance-working-with-broadcom-develop-advanced-ai-chip-sources-say-2024-06-24/</link><description>两位知情人士称，中国字节跳动正在与美国芯片设计商博通合作开发先进的人工智能处理器，此举将有助于 TikTok 的所有者在中美关系紧张之际确保充足的高端芯片供应。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 03:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-bytedance-working-with-broadcom-develop-advanced-ai-chip-sources-say-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统在中国威胁分裂主义后称独裁是“邪恶的”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/autocracy-is-evil-taiwan-president-says-after-china-threatens-death-separatism-2024-06-24/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周一在中国威胁要对“顽固”台独分裂分子判处死刑后表示，民主不是犯罪，独裁才是真正的“罪恶”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/autocracy-is-evil-taiwan-president-says-after-china-threatens-death-separatism-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>1-5月我国财政收入下降2.8%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-fiscal-revenue-drops-28-january-may-2024-06-24/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，由于需求疲软拖累经济复苏，2024年前5个月中国财政收入同比下降2.8%，较1-4月下降2.7%加速。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-fiscal-revenue-drops-28-january-may-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望欧盟在谈判开始时取消电动汽车关税计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-wants-eu-scrap-ev-tariffs-evs-by-july-4-chinese-state-media-reports-2024-06-24/</link><description>据中国官方媒体《环球时报》报道，在双方同意就可能的妥协进行谈判后，北京希望欧盟在 7 月 4 日之前取消对中国电动汽车进口征收初步关税的计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-wants-eu-scrap-ev-tariffs-evs-by-july-4-chinese-state-media-reports-2024-06-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>